title: 278: Jets/Colts trade fallout, Interview with TE Hayden Hurst
itunes:title: 278: Jets/Colts trade fallout, Interview with TE Hayden Hurst
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap the blockbuster trade between the New York Jets and Indianapolis Colts and how it shakes up the draft (1:01). The guys also review a few of the toughest players in this draft class to evaluate (35:20) before they sit down with the top tight end prospect, South Carolina's Hayden Hurst (40:57).
